# Kitchen Dashboard Test Plan

## Step 1: Place an Order
- [ ] Navigate to `http://localhost:8080/index.html?table=T4`
- [ ] Add "Koshari" to order
- [ ] Add "Molokhia with Chicken" to order
- [ ] Enter name "Ramo"
- [ ] Enter notes "No onions on the Koshari please"
- [ ] Select "Cash" payment
- [ ] Click "Place Order"

## Step 2: Send Order to Kitchen (Cashier Dashboard)
- [ ] Navigate to `http://localhost:8080/dashboard/cashier.html`
- [ ] Find order and click "Send to Kitchen"
- [ ] Verify order disappears from cashier view

## Step 3: Verify Kitchen Dashboard
- [ ] Navigate to `http://localhost:8080/dashboard/kitchen.html`
- [ ] Verify Order Number (prominent), Table (T4), Customer (Ramo)
- [ ] Verify Items (Koshari, Molokhia with Chicken) - No prices
- [ ] Verify Notes Block ("No onions on the Koshari please")
- [ ] Verify Elapsed Time counter
- [ ] Verify Order Counter in top bar
- [ ] Click "Order Ready — Notify Waiter"
- [ ] Verify card disappears and counter updates
